Wrapper class around the food object and its necessary details.

Data txt file referenced by DataBase now  put in its resource directory as per current Gradle specifications (main/resource). ClassPathing used to access this data in init method.

Update tests to use getFat() instead

FoodEntry child class that supports datetime functionality.

- FoodList returns List for public methods. Tweak to calculator to accept List instead of ArrayList made.

- List function class added to contain constantly reused FP methods on lists.
Some computers execute too quickly such that there is not neglible difference in time elapsed. Added a short 1 second sleep to prevent this from causing errors.
Executing too quickly affects use of LocalDateTime.now() in tests.
